      <title>世界第二大柑橘出口国南非发现芽腐病</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/world-s-no-2-citrus-exporter-south-africa-detects-bud-rot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非是继西班牙之后全球最大的柑橘出口国，该国官员在两个省的商业木瓜园中发现了芽腐病，并警告农民在移动植物时要小心，以防止病害蔓延。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/world-s-no-2-citrus-exporter-south-africa-detects-bud-rot</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 10:09:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
