    <item>
      <title>德国可能需要比计划更长时间保留备用燃煤电厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/germany-may-need-to-keep-reserve-coal-plants-longer-than-planned</link>
      <description><![CDATA[电网运营商 Amprion GmbH 警告称，由于新天然气电厂建设进度严重落后于计划，德国可能需要比预期更长时间地保留其闲置的燃煤电厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/germany-may-need-to-keep-reserve-coal-plants-longer-than-planned</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 09:49:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国放宽长期资金规则以提振股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/china-eases-rules-for-long-term-funds-to-support-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国推出了一揽子措施稳定股市，其中包括计划增加养老金对国内上市公司的投资额度，以应对唐纳德·特朗普第二任总统任期内的不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/china-eases-rules-for-long-term-funds-to-support-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 09:20:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
